<TEXT>
<P>
COLOMBO, December 7 (Xinhua) -- The Sri Lankan Foreign
Ministry, in collaboration with the University of Colombo, has set
up a new site on the World Wide Web (WWW) in a bid to promote the
national image of the country.
</P>
