incandescent bulbs, will be 15, 20, and 30 watts.
</P>
<P>
Brazilian Energy and Mines Minister Raimundo Brito estimates
that the country could save 700 megawatts of energy by using the
compact fluorescent lamps.
</P>
<P>
The lamps, besides saving energy, have a life of 10,000 hours,
while the conventional incandescent lamps only last 1,000 hours.
</P>
